<title>Obsidian 1.4.16 Mobile (Public)</title>
<link href="https://obsidian.md/changelog/2023-10-13-mobile-v1.4.16/"/>
<updated>2023-10-13T00:00:00Z</updated>
<id>https://obsidian.md/changelog/2023-10-13-mobile-v1.4.16/</id>
<content type="html"><ul> <li>Includes all new functionality and bug fixes up to <a href="https://obsidian.md/changelog/2023-10-13-desktop-v1.4.16/">Obsidian Desktop v1.4.16</a>.</li> <li>Fixed drag and drop handler on iOS causing the view to scroll. This affects properties, the mobile toolbar, and the font picker.</li> <li>Added a &quot;Create&quot; button to menus like the share menu.</li> <li>Updated formatting of share menu and fixed bug where it would fail to insert if current file was in reading mode.</li> <li>Lots of styling improvements for settings.</li> <li>Login screen no longer mentions requiring 2FA if it is not enabled on your account.</li> <li>Fixed bug where template properties wouldn't get applied if a value was <code>null</code>.</li> <li>Fixed issue where you could sometimes not add text after an image in Live Preview.</li> <li>iOS: Added new persistent &quot;Hide keyboard&quot; button to the mobile toolbar.</li> <li>Canvas: Fixed Canvas view not being focused on touch.</li> </ul> <h2>Phone-only Improvements</h2> <ul> <li>Suggestions will now appear inline below the cursor instead of attached to the keyboard.</li> <li>Closing app settings no longer causes double animation.</li> <li>Fixed loading bar when opening the community themes and community plugins directory.</li> </ul> </content>
