<updated>2022-08-31T00:00:00Z</updated>
<id>https://obsidian.md/changelog/2022-08-31-desktop-v0.16.1/</id>
<content type="html"><h2>Improvements</h2> <ul> <li>The setting <strong>Appearance → Show view header</strong> has been renamed to <strong>Appearance → <em>Show tab title bar</em></strong>.</li> <li>The setting <strong>Appearance → Title bar style</strong> has been renamed to <strong>Appearance → <em>Window frame style</em></strong>.</li> <li>Added &quot;UI zoom level&quot; slider to <strong>Settings → Appearance</strong>.</li> <li>Release notes will now automatically show after Obsidian updates.</li> <li>Improved community theme/plugin README.md relative images, added support for videos.</li> <li>Added default hotkey for opening link in new window (<code>Ctrl/Cmd+Alt+Shift+Enter</code>)</li> <li>Improved performance for installing/updating plugins.</li> <li>Reduced flashing when searching for plugins.</li> <li>Renamed &quot;active file&quot; to &quot;current file&quot; in several commands for better consistency.</li> </ul> <h2>No longer broken</h2> <ul> <li>Fixed quick switcher's &quot;open to the right&quot; hotkey not working.</li> <li>Fixed &quot;Backlink in document&quot; not always updating.</li> <li>Fixed file explorer not always highlighting selected files.</li> <li>Tweaked sizing and positioning of title bar when zoomed in/out.</li> <li>Obsidian Sync will now avoid deleting old themes.</li> <li>Fixed misaligned logo in custom mode.</li> <li>Fixed status bar jitter when word count updates.</li> <li>macOS: Tweaked location of traffic lights when zoomed in/out.</li> </ul> </content>
</entry>
