<content type="html"><ul> <li>New &quot;Quick Action&quot; pull down from the top, defaults to Command Palette, but can be configured.</li> <li>Completely revamped left and right sidebar animation.</li> <li>Setting and Switch vault buttons have been moved to the bottom of the ribbon (just like the desktop layout).</li> <li>Slight improvement to link and tag suggestions so the text is less likely to be hidden behind the panel.</li> <li>Tab and Shift-Tab now works.</li> <li>Readable line length is now implemented in edit mode.</li> <li>Fixed fold indicators not visible in preview. (Edit mode still not implemented yet).</li> <li>Obsidian Publish is now available from mobile.</li> <li>Desktop-only plugins can no longer be installed.</li> <li>Fixed resize handle visible through side panes.</li> <li>Fixed long vault names don't look very nice.</li> <li>Also includes everything up to Desktop v0.11.13</li> </ul> </content>
