<content type="html"><ul> <li>Improved iCloud performance (Should no longer lag or freeze).</li> <li>You can now add local Obsidian vaults, sub folders, and files to other apps in Files.</li> <li>Improved Obsidian Sync reliability.</li> </ul> </content>
